ActGeneral Campaign Star and General Service Medal Regulations, 2009
SubjectOrder Awarding of the General Service Medal with the ALLIED FORCE ribbon
PrecisOrder (a) repealing Orders in Council P.C. 2004-754 of June 17, 2004 and P.C. 2007-383 of March 22, 2007; (b) determining who has rendered service that is worthy of recognition by the award of the General Service Medal with the ALLIED FORCE ribbon (service in Aviano, Vicenza or Skopje); and (c) establishing its order of precedence in the Canadian Honours System.
